title: [Icemule Trace, Exterior]
description: A red brick chimney peeks above the high stone walls of Icemule Trace.  The laughter of children rings clearly in the crisp air.  A plume of white smoke billows overhead, fading to a mere pinpoint in the sunlit sky.

A red brick chimney peeks above the high stone walls of Icemule Trace.  The calm and quiet of the night settles like a blanket on the immediate area.  A plume of white smoke billows overhead, fading to a mere pinpoint in the moonlit sky.
